{
  "_comment": [
    "Root-level Claude Code workspace MCP config — copy this file to .mcp.json.",
    ".mcp.json is gitignored. Never commit it.",
    "",
    "Quick start:",
    "  1. npm install -g rails-mcp-server",
    "  2. bin/foundry export-secrets    (writes STRIPE_API_KEY to .env.local)",
    "  3. source .env.local             (or configure direnv)",
    "  4. cp .mcp.json.example .mcp.json",
    "  5. Restart your agent (Claude Code / Cursor / etc.)",
    "",
    "See .mcp/ for per-client examples (Claude Desktop, Cursor, VS Code).",
    "See docs/ai/MCP.md for full architecture docs."
  ],
  "mcpServers": {
    "rails": {
      "command": "bin/mcp"
    },
    "stripe": {
      "command": "stripe-mcp",
      "env": {
        "STRIPE_API_KEY": "${STRIPE_API_KEY}"
      }
    }
  }
}
